    <releases>
        <release date="2024-05-15" version="0.9.2">
            <description>
                <p>A new release is here with some new features, bug fixes and improvements:</p>
                <p>New features:</p>
                <ul>
                    <ui>Automatic ordered list support</ui>
                </ul>
                <p>Bug fixes and improvements:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Much smoother scrolling on Windows and Linux</li>
                    <li>Fixed issue with closing/expanding panes via horizontal swipe</li>
                    <li>You can now delete an image by pressing the delete/backspace key</li>
                    <li>Fixed an issue with the cursor not appearing at the right location after pressing return</li>
                    <li>Huge performance boost when handling very large notes</li>
                    <li>Fixed an issue on Windows and Linux where the window didn't show the native title bar</li>
                    <li>Fixed an issue when moving selected blocks up/down using keyboard shortcuts and the editor lost focus</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
    <release date="2024-05-11" version="0.9.1">
            <description>
                <p>A new release is here with some bug fixes and improvements:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix DropCap getting too big when resizing</li>
                    <li>Disable folders pane animation for now (some users reported jittery animation)</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>

        <release date="2023-05-01" version="0.9.0">
            <description>
                <p>Initial release.</p>
            </description>
        </release>
    </releases>
